                     NLRB sets April 4-5 as election dates

   February 28, 2022

Highlights

     o April 4-5 will be the dates for an NLRB-run election to decide whether
       some MIT graduate students will form a union affiliated with the
       United Electrical, Radio and Machine Workers of America (UE).
     o The proposed union now includes about 3,750 of MIT's 7,000 graduate
